  "title": "Project Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Support Project Manager on site execution, coordinate project management activities, resources, equipment, and information.</li>\n  <li>Monitor work progress, handle any issue that arise and ensure they can complete on schedule.</li>\n  <li>Prepare daily site progress reports, schedule, co-ordinate and monitor the assigned projects.</li>\n  <li>Attend kick-off meeting, site meeting, site walk and brief by clients, officers &amp; etc.</li>\n  <li>Ensure workers do proper housekeeping daily to maintains safe and clean working environment. And compile with onsite Workplace Safety and Health regulations.</li>\n  <li>Ensure all the permit, machinery and materials needed on site is ready and machinery is in working condition before start work.</li>\n  <li>Ad-hoc matters as assigned by the PM which is necessary for the execution of the project</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of working experience as supervisor/ Coordinator in construction ndustry / project site work</li>\n  <li>Possess Certificate in building construction supervisor’s safety</li>\n  <li>Preferably with Class 3 Driving licence.</li>\n  <li>Good Interpersonal and Communication skills. Leadership, Problem-solving and multi-tasking skills</li>\n  <li>Profound knowledge of construction safety regulations and workflow sequence till handover.</li>\n</ul>",
